XXE Attacks on Vulnerable XML APIs
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Understand XML External Entity (XXE) vulnerabilities and their security impact
Identify and exploit XXE vulnerabilities in XML-processing APIs
Implement various XXE attack techniques including file disclosure and SSRF
Develop Python scripts to automate XXE payload generation and testing
Apply proper defenses against XXE attacks in web applications
